ActElectoral Boundaries Readjustment Act
SubjectOrder Directing that a Proclamation be Issued Declaring the Representation Order to be in Force
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue declaring to be in force the REPRESENTATION ORDER effective on the first dissolution of Parliament that occurs at least seven months after the day on which the Proclamation is issued.
